data.eml:eml: Two new species of amphibian nematodes from Bhadra Wildlife Sanctuary, Western Ghats, India.

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Rizvi, Anjum Nasreen (2009): Two new species of amphibian nematodes from Bhadra Wildlife Sanctuary, Western Ghats, India. Zootaxa 2013: 58-68, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.185867
